---
// Beyond Work Section (Asymmetric Magazine Layout)
---

<section id="beyond-work" class="beyond-work">
  <div class="section-layout">
    <div class="section-sidebar">
      <div class="sticky-title fade-in-up">
        <h2 class="section-title">Beyond Work</h2>
        <p>审美与能量的来源</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-content">
      <div class="magazine-grid">
        <!-- Aesthetics (Photography/Art) -->
        <div class="grid-item aesthetics fade-in-up" data-tone="beyond-aesthetics">
          <div class="image-wrapper bg-placeholder"></div>
          <div class="caption">
            <h3>Lens & Canvas</h3>
            <p>捕捉光线与构图的平衡。长期的视觉训练让我对克制感、材质与排版更敏感，这直接影响了我对产品体验的判断。</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Energy (Running/Cycling) -->
        <div class="grid-item energy fade-in-up" data-tone="beyond-energy">
          <div class="image-wrapper small bg-placeholder"></div>
          <div class="caption">
            <h3>100km & 800m</h3>
            <p>
              曾把共享单车从紫金港骑到海宁（100公里），也拿过校运会800米冠军。
              运动对我来说不是“标签”，而是一种建立耐心、输出稳定性的长期主义训练。
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .beyond-work {
    display: block;
  }

  .section-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .section-layout {
      grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
    }
    
    .sticky-title {
      position: sticky;
      top: calc(var(--header-height) + var(--space-xl));
    }
  }

  .section-title {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 3rem);
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .magazine-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .image-wrapper {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    background-color: var(--color-border);
    transition: transform var(--transition-bounce);
  }

  .image-wrapper:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px) scale(1.01);
  }

  .image-wrapper.small {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
  }

  .grid-item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-rows: auto 1fr;
    align-content: start;
    min-height: 100%;
  }

  .grid-item[data-tone] .caption h3 {
    color: var(--tone-strong);
  }

  .grid-item[data-tone] .caption p {
    color: var(--tone-muted);
  }

  .caption {
    margin-top: var(--space-sm);
    width: 100%;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }

  .caption h3 {
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  }

  .energy.fade-in-up {
    transition-delay: 0.2s;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .magazine-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-md);
    }
    
    .image-wrapper.small {
      width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
